mean_cn: adj. 早产的，过早的，早熟的；  n. 早产儿
mean_en: (of a birth or a baby) happening or being born before the normal length of pregnancy has been completed
sentence: The premature baby was so small that it was put into an incubator.
sentence_trans: 这个早产的婴儿太小了，被放到了保温箱里。
word_etyma: pre预先 + mature成熟 → premature比预期时间早的，仓促的
